            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The position sensitive silicon detector array",
                "for alpha particles was positioned in the forward",
                "hemisphere, covering distances between 942 to 1292 mm",
