              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SI",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " To detect and identify the recoiling",
                "boron ions, a set of silicon-detector telescopes was",
                "placed on the solenoid axis between the target and",
                "the light-charged-particle detector array. The recoil",
                "telescopes subtended laboratory polar angles between",
                "1.0 and 5.6 deg and 92% of the azimuthal angle range"
              ]
